items.badge_description: Lovers of little green cones rejoice. National IPA Day is pretty much like your best birthday! Whether you love hazies, milkshake, double, triple, or even quad IPAs just check in one today to earn this coveted badge.

A global celebration of beer, International Beer Day toasts to beers from all across the globe. Like a helles from Germany, a tripel from Belgian, or an ESB from Britain. Cheers to you, wherever you might be in the world!

Looking for more kick than a session beer, but want to be able to stay for a few rounds? You have to keep it in the middle. That's 85 beers with an ABV greater than 5% and less than 10%. Try 5 more for Level 18!
It takes the perfect amount of light, the right framing and a touch of creative love to get the perfect picture of your brew. Now its time to drink it! Thats 15 check-ins with a photo.

There's beer in them thar hills! You're setting off on your journey through the world of beer, but be sure to take a little time to get to know each brewery as you go. That's a beer from 45 different breweries. Try 5 more for Level 10!
